---
import '@/styles/global.css';
import LightHeaderClient from '@/components/ui/islands/LightHeaderClient';
import Footer from '@/components/ui/Footer.astro';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Privacy Policy | Centerline Flight Training</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Privacy Policy for Centerline Flight Training - How we collect, use, and protect your personal information." />
    
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="https://pub-b9b491aee0b94c2c8e6c5d1dde4848db.r2.dev/public/images/logo/apple-touch-icon.png" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="96x96" href="https://pub-b9b491aee0b94c2c8e6c5d1dde4848db.r2.dev/public/images/logo/favicon-96x96.png" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="https://pub-b9b491aee0b94c2c8e6c5d1dde4848db.r2.dev/public/images/logo/favicon.ico" />
  </head>

  <body class="overflow-x-hidden bg-gray-50">
    <!-- Header -->
    <LightHeaderClient client:load />

    <!-- Privacy Policy Content -->
    <section class="pt-32 pb-20 min-h-screen">
      <div class="max-w-[900px] mx-auto px-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-6 font-heading">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-12 font-heading">
          Last Updated: November 19, 2024
        </p>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-8">
          <!-- Introduction -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4 font-heading">1. Introduction</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-heading">
              Centerline Aviation INC ("Centerline Flight Training," "we," "us," or "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or use our services.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Information We Collect -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4 font-heading">2. Information We Collect</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-3 mt-6 font-heading">Personal Information</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-heading mb-4">
              We may collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us, including:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 font-heading">
              <li>Name and contact information (email, phone number, address)</li>
              <li>Date of birth and age verification</li>
              <li>Medical certificate information (as required by FAA)</li>
              <li>Payment and billing information</li>
              <li>Flight training records and progress</li>
              <li>Government-issued identification</li>
              <li>Emergency contact information</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-3 mt-6 font-heading">Automatically Collected Information</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-heading mb-4">
              When you visit our website, we may automatically collect:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 font-heading">
              <li>IP address and browser information</li>
              <li>Device type and operating system</li>
              <li>Pages visited and time spent on our site</li>
              <li>Referring website addresses</li>
              <li>Cookies and similar tracking technologies</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- How We Use Information -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4 font-heading">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-heading mb-4">
              We use the information we collect to:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 font-heading">
              <li>Provide and manage flight training services</li>
              <li>Process payments and maintain billing records</li>
              <li>Comply with FAA regulations and recordkeeping requirements</li>
              <li>Communicate with you about scheduling, training progress, and updates</li>
              <li>Respond to your inquiries and provide customer support</li>
              <li>Improve our services and website functionality</li>
              <li>Send promotional materials (with your consent)</li>
              <li>Ensure safety and security of our operations</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Information Sharing -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4 font-heading">4. How We Share Your Information</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-heading mb-4">
              We may share your information with:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 font-heading">
              <li><strong>Federal Aviation Administration (FAA):</strong> As required by law for training records and certification</li>
              <li><strong>Insurance Providers:</strong> For coverage and claims processing</li>
              <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Third-party vendors who assist in operations (payment processors, scheduling software, etc.)</li>
              <li><strong>Legal Authorities:</strong> When required by law or to protect our rights and safety</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-heading mt-4">
              We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties for marketing purposes.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- SMS Communications -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4 font-heading">5. SMS and Text Message Communications</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-heading">
              By providing your phone number and consenting to receive text messages, you agree to receive SMS communications from Centerline Flight Training regarding your flight training, scheduling updates, and service-related information. Message and data rates may apply. You can opt-out at any time by replying STOP to any text message or contacting us directly. Your consent to receive text messages is not a condition of purchasing our services.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Data Security -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4 font-heading">6. Data Security</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-heading">
              We implement appropriate technical and organizational security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Data Retention -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4 font-heading">7. Data Retention</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-heading">
              We retain your personal information for as long as necessary to provide our services and comply with legal obligations. Flight training records are maintained in accordance with FAA regulations, which require retention for specified periods.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Your Rights -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4 font-heading">8. Your Privacy Rights</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-heading mb-4">
              You have the right to:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 font-heading">
              <li>Access and review your personal information</li>
              <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
              <li>Request deletion of your information (subject to legal requirements)</li>
              <li>Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
              <li>Withdraw consent for SMS communications</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-heading mt-4">
              To exercise these rights, please contact us using the information provided below.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Cookies -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4 font-heading">9. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-heading">
              Our website uses cookies and similar technologies to enhance your browsing experience, analyze site traffic, and understand where our visitors are coming from. You can control cookies through your browser settings, but disabling cookies may affect website functionality.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Children's Privacy -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4 font-heading">10. Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-heading">
              Our services are not directed to children under 13. While students aged 14-17 may participate in flight training with parental consent, we do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 without verified parental consent.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Changes to Policy -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4 font-heading">11. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-heading">
              We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last Updated" date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Contact -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4 font-heading">12. Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-heading">
              If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at:
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 text-gray-700 font-heading">
              <p>Centerline Aviation INC</p>
              <p>2050 N 300 W, Hangar #122</p>
              <p>Spanish Fork, UT 84660</p>
              <p class="mt-2">Phone: (801) 477-0418</p>
              <p>Email: contact@centerlineaviationinc.com</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

